wireframes.name: Name of Wireframe
wireframes.ownerId: documentID of Owner in users field
wireframes.editing: true if editing, false if not
wireframes.selected: int key to control that is currently selected. If none selected, -1

properties.text: text in the control. Only available in button|textfield|label
properties.fontColor: hex color of text in the control. Only available in button|textfield|label
properties.fontSize: number size of text in the control. Only available in button|textfield|label
